race.description: Fuller Fitness All Stars Sprint H
race.comment: ASTON NERO (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his sharp win the start prior, getting around Mandurah over 400m in 22.38. Expected to push the clock again here. MAILATA (8) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.75 lengths back in third (29.86) at this track in a Free For All over 520m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading chance. TIMMY TESLA (7) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (30.56) there two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Has a strong record from this draw, notching four wins and four minor placings from eight starts. Can figure in the finish. WEST ON SIDNEY (6) warrants respect with the drop in trip.
